I"Ó<h4 id="what-is-termuxx11-">What is Termux:x11 ?</h4>
<p>As name suggest ‚ÄúX11‚Äù it is another addon of termux, which is quite useful when you want to use GUI application like any Desktop environment,this addon did‚Äôt released yet (20 may 2020) because of some minor issue, i hope it will release soon.</p>

<h4 id="why-termuxx11-">Why Termux:x11 ?</h4>
<p>Termux:x11 should exist because termux does‚Äôt support graphics,that‚Äôs why  in order to use GUI application from termux.</p>

<p>it use wayland protocol and has many advantages over X
for more info, have a look <a href="https://askubuntu.com/questions/11537/why-is-wayland-better">here</a></p>

<h4 id="install-termuxx11">Install Termux:x11</h4>
<p>Since it did‚Äôt release yet, even then you can install it,if you have installed you can skip this part</p>

<h6 id="backup-your-data">Backup your data,</h6>
<p>You have to uninstalled all addon and termux app to install it, because right now termux:x11 is not available in playstore or fdroid.
you know that, any if termux application can‚Äôt be install if signature is different.</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
